{"tid":1560262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老成日話班後生搞事,我心諗真係影響到你咩?","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:31.000Z","uid":119688,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"707978539d7667e63e55ac6159a75785ebe963d9","tid":1560262,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"唔支持任何犯法同暴力行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我針對廢老成日話人搞事<br />\n真心影響到佢地咩<br />\n佢地都唔撚出街/出遠門<br />\n日日擔住枝煙係樓下公園<br />\n周圍吐痰 砍酒捉棋賭錢<br />\n烏煙障氣<br />\n衰d講句<br />\n都係等緊鬼頭馬面黎接你姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1686468add9c760334478673584fc76db9354395","tid":1560262,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"原來死線係10月1號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560249</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c71cef9448124bf2142cb4ed1273eedcbc68b19","tid":1560262,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"劈酒？砍酒？<br />\nbtw，廢老都係得把口，啲愛國廢中先真心弱智"},{"pid":"2792ee9d3be47dc8940587fca6fd134d4a14b0d3","tid":1560262,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"